\label{lem:SingPn}
For any $a\in\Sing(\P_n)\cup\{1\}$ we have
\[
a = e_1\cdots e_k \qquad\text{for some $e_1,\ldots,e_k\in E_0(\P_n)$ with $\Phi(e_1,\ldots,e_k) = 0$.}
